#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_candles/init.lua:71
msgid ""
"A candle is a block that emits light when lit with a flint and steel. It "
"comes in the sixteen dye colors. Up to four of the same color of candle can "
"be placed in one block space, which affects the amount of light produced."
msgstr ""

